+<!-- Formatting note: terminate all comments with a period, to avoid breaking
+     the documentation output. To suppress comment lines from the documentation
+     output, insert an eat-comment element after the comment lines.
+-->
+
+<resources>
+    <plurals name="type_clock_header">
+        <item quantity="other"><annotation name="color">It’s</annotation>"
+^1
+^2"</item>
+        <item quantity="one"><annotation name="color">It’s</annotation>"
+^1
+^2"</item>
+        <item quantity="few"><annotation name="color">It’s</annotation>"
+^1
+^2"</item>
+     </plurals>
+
+    <!-- Skeleton string format for displaying the date with number. -->
+    <string name="abbrev_wday_day_no_year">eeeedd</string>
+
+    <!-- Skeleton string format for displaying the date. -->
+    <string name="abbrev_wday_no_year">eeee</string>
+
+    <!-- Skeleton string format for displaying the day of the month. -->
+    <string name="abbrev_wday_month_no_year">MMMMd</string>
+</resources>
